room_title: Escape room "Like a Surgeon" by Make a Break Escape in Tampa
room_description: With the President of the United States in town, a lone gunman has chosen to strike and has gone on a shooting spree. The hospital nearby has been put on lockdown, and you are a group of surgeons, trapped inside an observation room with an unknown patient on the table. You must find a way to get into the operating room, identify the patient, their condition, and save them before time runs out!
